birdcage boy
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a used-car dealer, descriptive of their outdoor `showrooms' in the 1950s, surrounded by heavy wire-mesh and barbed wire for security against thieves of the highly sought-after used cars
Origin: [none]
